st university of illinois at urbanachampaign indian institute of technology bombay iitbmonash research academy indraprastha institute of information technology delhi indian institute of science bangalore purdue university indian institute of information technology bangalore infosys prizeedit the infosys prize is an annual award given to scientists researchers engineers and social scientists connected to india it is given by the infosys science foundation a nonprofit trust which was set up in february  by infosys and some members of its board the prize is given under six categories each category includes a gold medallion a citation certificate and prize money of ₹ million us infosys confluenceedit infosys confluence is an annual flagship event by infosys which hosts visionaries distinguished industry thought leaders  innovators on one platform the second edition of this event is being held from may rd to th  in san francisco employeesedit the development center in mysuru campus infosys has a total of  employees as of  january  of which  were women its workforce consists of employees representing  nationalities working from  countries  countries as per the base location out of its total workforce  are software professionals  are working in its bpo arm and remaining  work for support and sales the attrition rate of infosys ltd excluding its subsidiaries for  months ending  september  was  and following the annual hike for employees during  the attrition rate is likely to increase during fy  infosys received  applications from prospective employees and had a gross addition of  employees a  hiring rate training centre in mysuruedit as the worlds largest corporate university the infosys global education centre in the  acre campus has  instructors and  classrooms with international benchmarks at its core established in  it had trained around  engineering graduates by june  it can train  employees at a given point of time on various technologies the infosys leadership insti