ani raghavan n s ashok arora and s d shibulal on july   and is headquartered in bangalore india company background infosys is indias secondlargest information technology service company it develops and maintains software for corporate customers and also provides a wide range of itrelated services including consulting the company serves customers in more than  countries and has a global workforce of more than  people of its consolidated sales more than  are generated in overseas markets including the us infosys symbolizes the indian it industrys rapid progress it was established with  capital in  by seven cofounders it grew in the s mainly by winning contracts to develop software and systems for overseas clients indias it industry attracted attention when they handled contracts related to the yk problem which was expected to lead to computer problems in  infosys rapidly moved up the ladder to become a global it business in  it became the first indian company to list on the nasdaq in new york cofounders and their families have a combined equity stake of more than  in infosys since the companys establishment four cofounders including narayana murthy served as ceos however in  vishal sikka a former executive at german software maker sap became the companys first ceo from outside the group of cofounders in the news reliance industries earnings new phone launch lead indian shares higher july    pm jst wipro to buy back  billion worth stocks profit beats estimates july    pm jst india stocks edge lower as earnings disappoint investors july    pm jst india shares post gains as drug makers itc advance july    pm jst infosys wipro lead india shares to record highs july    pm jst asia markets nikkei asia index extends gains on bets us rate hike likely delayed july    pm jst nikkei asia index extends gains on bets us rate hike likely delayed july    pm jst more news for infosys ltd financial highlights mar  local currency us dollar revenue m gross profit m operating income m in