ivalent to ₹ or us in  per share against book value of ₹ equivalent to ₹ or us in  per share the infosys ipo was under subscribed but it was bailed out by us investment bank morgan stanley which picked up   of equity at the offer price its shares were listed in stock exchanges in june  with trading opening at ₹ equivalent to ₹ or us in  per share in october  it made a private placement of  shares at ₹ equivalent to ₹ or us in  each against book value of ₹ equivalent to ₹ or ¢ us in  per share to foreign institutional investors fiis financial institutions fis and corporates in march  it issued  adss equivalent to  equity shares of par value of ₹ equivalent to ₹ or ¢ us in  each at us equivalent to  in  per ads under the american depositary shares program and the same were listed on the nasdaq national market in us the total issue amount was us million the share price surged to ₹ equivalent to ₹ or us in  by  making it the costliest share on the market at the time at that time infosys was among the  biggest companies by market capitalization on the nasdaq during july  june  and november  it made secondary ads issues of us equivalent to  in  million us equivalent to  in  billion and us equivalent to  in  billion respectively in december  infosys transferred the listing of its american depositary shares ads from the nasdaq to the nyse in july  infosys started a product subsidiary called edgeverve systems focusing on enterprise software products for business operations customer service procurement and commerce network domains in august  the finacle global banking solutions assets were officially transferred from infosys and became part of the product company edgeverve systems product portfolio the credit rating of the company is a given by standard  poors on dec in february  infosys announced it would acquire the us automation technology company panaya for around  million operationsedit headquarters of infosys in bengaluru on  january  infosys had  clients across  countr